com.nokia.maps.component.gesture

Class LongTouchComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nokia.maps.component.AbstractMapComponent
      • com.nokia.maps.component.touch.TouchComponent
        • com.nokia.maps.component.gesture.LongTouchComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MapComponent
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GestureLongTouch, TimerLongTouch

    public abstract class LongTouchComponent
extends TouchComponent
    This class offers an abstract base class for long touch components which fire a Command if a Long Press has occurred, the class also remembers the location where the long press occurred.

      • isActive

        protected boolean isActive(int x,
               int y)
        This method retrieves a boolean value indicating whether the LongTouchComponent is active. By default the component is always active and reacts to LongPresses anywhere.
        Specified by:
        isActive in class TouchComponent
        Parameters:
        x - x axis pixel coordinate on the screen that has been touched.
        y - y axis pixel coordinate on the screen that has been touched.
        Returns:
        true, Since the Long press reacts to the whole screen, the component is always active.
